  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "DevOps Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Deegit Asia is seeking a skilled and proactive DevOps Engineer to design, implement, and manage CI/CD pipelines, cloud infrastructure, and automation processes. The ideal candidate will work closely with development, QA, and operations teams to ensure high availability, scalability, security, and performance of applications and platforms.<br /><br /><strong>Role Overview – Infrastructure & DevOps Engineer:</strong><br />\nAs an Infrastructure and DevOps Engineer, you will be responsible for defining requirements, designing, building, and testing cloud infrastructure components, primarily on the Azure platform (and AWS where applicable). You are expected to act as a subject matter expert, collaborate closely with cross-functional teams, and contribute to key technical and architectural decisions.</p><p>The role requires strong hands-on expertise in cloud infrastructure, DevOps engineering practices, and automation. You will also support team decision-making, engage with multiple stakeholders, and provide scalable and secure solutions across projects.</p><p><strong>Key Skills & Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Design, build, and configure cloud services (Azure / AWS) to improve operational efficiency and security</li><li>Apply and promote best practices in cloud infrastructure and DevOps methodologies</li><li>Implement and manage infrastructure using Terraform on Azure and/or AWS</li><li>Administer and support Microsoft Azure environments (for Azure role)</li><li>Evaluate and integrate new technologies to enhance existing systems and processes</li><li>Facilitate effective cross-team communication to ensure alignment on goals and deliverables</li></ul>",
